p0001 = "GREAT COMPLINE"
p0002 = "The office of Compline is not sung in the Church in the Monastery of the Lavra, but one reads it in one\u2019s cell. In the Koinovia of Palestine, however, Compline is sung as follows."
p0003 = "About the 12th hour of the day the Lamplighter enters and having made a metania to the Superior he strikes the simandron 12 times and we assemble in the Church. Each makes the prescribed metanias and we sit for a little until all, or most, are assembled. The Priest rises from his seat and having made the customary metania to the Abbot he gives the blessing. After the blessing by the Priest, the Superior, or the Reader, continues"
